response.headline: Ichiran Ramen headquarters location and details in Fukuoka, Japan
response.summary: Ichiran Shisha Honcha is the Ichiran Ramen headquarters located in Fukuoka, Japan at 5 Chome-3-2 Nakasu, Hakata Ward. This original location is considered the birthplace of tonkotsu ramen, operates 24/7, and only the first two floors are dedicated to the restaurant despite common misconceptions about the entire building.

location_tags: Fukuoka, Japan (5 Chome-3-2 Nakasu, Hakata Ward, Fukuoka, 810-0801, Japan)

Operating Hours: Open 24 hours a day, seven days a week
